data.description: Welcome to your new home! Motivated Sellers offering 2/1 loan buydown incentive.  Ask us how this works to save you $$!  This charming 2004 home in Railroad Springs boasts a split & open floorplan, with a 2-car garage. The 3 bedrooms, 2 baths provide plenty of space for everyone.  The fully fenced yard with custom landscaping.  Enjoy the community hiking trails, a basketball court, and playgrounds. Plus, you're just moments away from shopping, I-40, I-17, Northern University, and WL Gore. Seize this chance for a vibrant, convenient lifestyle!
